{"tid":1631941,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［重整旗鼓］和勇再connect","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T01:51:05.000Z","uid":260093,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e44cd805a8c39710b7af110f52a8a1b0fd506aec","tid":1631941,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:58.000Z","msg":"<ins>勇武</ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 今日有唔少手足失控嘅觀感，前線手足請謹記我哋成埸運動嘅目的 &mdash; <span style=\"color: gold;\">「對準政權」&amp; 「五大訴求，缺一不可」</span>。所有行動須圍繞哩兩個目的進行。<br />\n<br />\n例如：破壞交通燈同拆欄做rb <br />\n           👉增加管治成本/壓力<br />\n           👉辛苦D PoPo 出嚟清埸<br />\n<br />\n2. 拆港鐵、黑店同美心產業商店係bonus，但<span style=\"color: blue;\">前線手足要明白，唔係個個香港人嘅道德底線都進化到同意你哋用火魔法，所以如果用返水魔法去進行「裝飾」會比較好感官少少，香港人亦都接受到，唔會成日郁啲就割蓆。</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 因為好多外國傳媒只會報道我哋破壞呢啲建築物同商店，唔會主動解釋當中嘅原因。建議有手足需要準備<span style=\"color: red;\">紙同筆，當傳媒影印手足進行「裝飾」嘅時候，喺隔離加以解釋，寫清楚咩原因我哋要咁做（建議中英文都有），呢張解釋紙一定要曝光係鏡頭面前！完事之後貼係現場！</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 鶳方面，<span style=\"color: gold;\">盡量唔好見血，感觀唔好！仲有唔該隔離都附上中英文解釋！</span><br />\n<br />\n5. 態度方面，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">請be humble be polite！</span><br />\n<br />\n6. 思想方面：<br />\n    ❌等和理非走先走<br />\n    ❌陣地<br />\n    ✅遊擊，起完，有狗即走<br />\n    撚狗屋唔係問題，要確保找得到！<br />\n<br />\n7. 安全方面：<br />\n     因為你哋帶着文具，比較敏感。<br />\n     除非你哋確定自己係等車&amp;搭車過程當中安全，唔會比狗截查，如果唔係唔建議你哋撤退之後即刻離開或者榴槤係街上，<span style=\"color: gold;\">建議你哋有商場入商場，或者去D黃店/大型連鎖店食下野先！</span><br />\n<br />\n8. 行動點到即止，個人應為唔使日日開花，做到嘅破壞做到晒就要停，例如：港鐵聽日又再停駛，咁咪等佢開返先再搞囉！啲黑紅店都未裝修返好，咁咪等佢裝修返好先再幫佢重新裝修過囉！<span style=\"color: green;\">日日搞對你哋身體同精神上都唔係咁好！感觀上比街坊都唔係咁好！</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>和理非</ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 麻煩幫手做好<span style=\"color: gold;\">地區及全球文宣工作</span>。建議繼續係連儂牆附近派傳單/放映會，目的係連結街坊，進行深黃色思想教育工作！同時<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該一人一個Twitter account ， 幫手retweet 同向世界解釋！</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 行動上，希望大家多啲cover 勇武！<span style=\"color: gold;\">做哨報位</span>，比前線知道啲popo位置，幫手搵路比前線離開！<span style=\"color: gold;\">可以的話，請提供埋暫托服務囉！</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 思想上，<span style=\"color: red;\">記住「核爆也不割」</span>！<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">遊行集會多啲出嚟，以人數表達一切！</span>"},{"pid":"a941e0098e59073b524dc91b0a5233224dd4ea1e","tid":1631941,"uid":310612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c36717f37ec14bb2045863c88db76c862edd633","tid":1631941,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a941e0098e59073b524dc91b0a5233224dd4ea1e","tid":1631941,"uid":310612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"大家都推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97da4a6ca00e6301afd07203d0678f3a73926fc","tid":1631941,"uid":207620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"撕了好難唔見血wo大佬"},{"pid":"e085ab3ec3082b8c6327842262880d5ad4f5137a","tid":1631941,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f97da4a6ca00e6301afd07203d0678f3a73926fc","tid":1631941,"uid":207620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"撕了好難唔見血wo大佬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:17.000Z","msg":"打關節位，踢春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c6cd70917abf5dbf3fb5b4883dd160a270a150","tid":1631941,"uid":306831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！"},{"pid":"cc4b9d3d6373d9513031fa9875073719f7406569","tid":1631941,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65c6cd70917abf5dbf3fb5b4883dd160a270a150","tid":1631941,"uid":306831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:53:50.000Z","msg":"我同你P牌仔都推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分享俾其他人幫手推啦！"},{"pid":"a1279873fbf2eae407eea81646eeaf7bf61fc742","tid":1631941,"uid":259973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"推。。。"},{"pid":"9bd5f6707b3c833003c81b915f5581ace9ecf19b","tid":1631941,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1279873fbf2eae407eea81646eeaf7bf61fc742","tid":1631941,"uid":259973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"推。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:02.000Z","msg":"都話P牌仔推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分享俾其他人幫手推，唔該你"},{"pid":"b3310a116762360cf1226709b080ddfae01b7c1c","tid":1631941,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:12:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1a6a59272000b6347dd6334e3b782e75e2c805e7","tid":1631941,"uid":70489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"以人數決定一切！！開花同遊行都要人！和理非勇武都要出"},{"pid":"f352cc5934aad00d6806e78921db0c26b5f1b64d","tid":1631941,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a6a59272000b6347dd6334e3b782e75e2c805e7","tid":1631941,"uid":70489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"以人數決定一切！！開花同遊行都要人！和理非勇武都要出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8297a0483f308358a5e0c8ffd184754bb1875523","tid":1631941,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:48:37.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3f4aee1faada8a5323597e0f65a32066f6f54e","tid":1631941,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:51:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1633005/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1633005/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">外國嘅人好幸福，一出世就生活係民主國家，有部分人根本唔會明點解我地爭取民主要用裝修、神獸（唔好高估外國人嘅智力，佢地睇野好表面）。</span><br />\n<br />\n有位巴講得好啱，我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">之所以漸漸少咗國際支持，係因為和理非戰場越來越細</span></span>。冇和理非嘅活動吸引佢地嘅眼球，餘下嘅只有神獸同裝修。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁所以，我地可以搞返個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">面具人鏈</span></span>，表達我地不畏反蒙面法，不畏極權嘅精神。<br />\n人鏈活動一直都比較少人被人拉，比起遊行更適合一家大細出席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且我地日日遊行，係外國人眼中好悶㗎。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">要有多啲gimmick佢地先會重新關注</span></span>。<br />\n時間、地點我唔知應該點定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但如果真係搞面具人鏈，我地可以帶上自製嘅四川面譜、facepainting、動物面膜、超人、Mario、多啦A夢、V煞⋯⋯冇嘅話純戴口罩都得，不過口罩上可以畫野。總之約精彩越好玩越好<br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">依家好需要一個嘉年華式抗爭</span></span>去緩和下大家嘅情緒，同獲得國際認同。好似之前雷射革命咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果各位手足覺得呢個建議ok，就開多另一個po去講時間地點啦。<br />\n（大家都要考慮一個問題就係，面具人鏈會唔會被狗拉，如果會嘅話⋯⋯都係諗諗先。畢竟expect一家大細出席，怕會全家被告）<br />\n<br />\np牌求推"}]}